<title>中方：强烈谴责、深切哀悼</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%EF%BC%9A%E5%BC%BA%E7%83%88%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E3%80%81%E6%B7%B1%E5%88%87%E5%93%80%E6%82%BC</link>
